SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
?x0 <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/fsisupp.owl#infrastructureDownstream> <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/CA_PPODterms.ttl#inf_f0b970> .
?x0 <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/fsisupp.owl#orgUser> ?x .
?x <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/fsisupp.owl#FSI_000239> <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/sustsource.owl#IS0010> .
?x a <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Organization> .
FILTER (?x != <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/CA_PPODterms.ttl#inf_f0b970>)
FILTER (?x != <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adhollander/FSLschemas/main/sustsource.owl#IS0010>)
}
